{"word":"νυστάζω","slug":"νυστάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νυστάζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to nod in sleep, to nap, slumber</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be sleepy, napping</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>dormito</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to hang the head</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}